19:52.200 --> 19:54.120
they sit down and wait

19:54.980 --> 19:56.420
when it is dark

19:56.420 --> 19:59.080
they hear and smell the zebra

19:59.080 --> 19:59.860
and the giraffe

19:59.860 --> 20:03.000
the man catches the giraffe

20:03.000 --> 20:05.200
ah now you're mine

20:05.200 --> 20:06.500
he says happily

20:06.500 --> 20:09.080
and the leopard catches the zebra

20:09.080 --> 20:10.920
and now you're mine

20:10.920 --> 20:11.980
he shouts

20:11.980 --> 20:13.500
looking at the zebra

20:14.200 --> 20:16.780
but there's something strange about these animals

20:16.780 --> 20:18.640
you're right

20:18.640 --> 20:19.860
says the man

20:20.640 --> 20:22.880
let's wait until morning and see

20:23.880 --> 20:25.280
the next morning

20:25.280 --> 20:26.640
the leopard and the man

20:26.640 --> 20:28.700
look at the two animals carefully

20:28.700 --> 20:30.200
what's this

20:30.200 --> 20:31.740
says the leopard

20:32.440 --> 20:33.920
a zebra with stripes

20:34.640 --> 20:36.620
and what's this

20:36.620 --> 20:38.020
says the man

20:38.280 --> 20:40.540
a giraffe with patches

20:41.640 --> 20:43.340
the leopard and the man

20:43.340 --> 20:44.540
are very surprised

20:44.540 --> 20:47.020
the giraffe and the zebra

20:47.020 --> 20:47.660
laugh

20:48.940 --> 20:50.640
why are you different?

20:51.340 --> 20:52.320
asks the leopard

20:52.820 --> 20:54.840
looking at the zebra and the giraffe

20:54.840 --> 20:56.740
please let us go

20:56.740 --> 20:58.600
and we can show you our trick

20:58.600 --> 20:59.940
says the giraffe

21:00.700 --> 21:02.400
yes show us

21:03.020 --> 21:04.800
say the leopard and the man

21:05.700 --> 21:07.500
the giraffe and the zebra

21:07.500 --> 21:09.660
go under the tall green trees

21:10.820 --> 21:13.100
suddenly the leopard and the man

21:13.100 --> 21:14.360
can't see them anymore

21:14.360 --> 21:16.580
where are you?

21:16.960 --> 21:17.940
asks the man

21:17.940 --> 21:20.640
the giraffe and the zebra laugh

21:23.260 --> 21:25.540
I can hear you laugh

21:25.540 --> 21:27.320
but I can't see you

21:27.320 --> 21:28.460
says the leopard

21:29.960 --> 21:31.580
laughs the giraffe

21:31.580 --> 21:33.500
where's your breakfast now?

21:34.480 --> 21:36.040
the leopard and the man

21:36.040 --> 21:38.000
don't know where they are

21:38.000 --> 21:41.500
we're here under the tall trees

21:42.200 --> 21:43.580
says the zebra

21:43.580 --> 21:45.460
but it's almost impossible

21:45.460 --> 21:47.700
to see us because we look like

21:47.700 --> 21:49.220
the shadows of the forest

21:49.220 --> 21:50.360
you're right

21:50.360 --> 21:51.660
says the leopard

21:52.400 --> 21:54.560
that's a very good trick

21:54.560 --> 21:55.820
says the man

21:56.540 --> 21:58.840
I think I need spots too

21:58.840 --> 22:00.100
says the leopard

22:01.380 --> 22:03.240
that's what bavian says

22:03.240 --> 22:04.560
and he's clever

22:05.460 --> 22:06.800
it's a good idea

22:06.800 --> 22:07.920
says the man

22:07.920 --> 22:10.640
it's more difficult to see you with spots

22:11.840 --> 22:14.140
the leopard goes into the forest

22:14.140 --> 22:16.620
and its shadows fall on him

22:16.620 --> 22:20.000
now he has dark spots on his body

22:20.000 --> 22:21.780
and they don't go away

22:22.780 --> 22:25.740
you've got some lovely dark spots

22:25.740 --> 22:27.620
all over your body

22:27.620 --> 22:29.260
says the man

22:29.840 --> 22:30.860
I like them

22:30.860 --> 22:32.080
says the leopard

22:32.080 --> 22:34.440
now I can hide in the forest

22:34.440 --> 22:36.480
like the giraffe and the zebra

22:36.480 --> 22:38.820
yes says the man

22:38.820 --> 22:42.240
now no one can find you in the forest

22:42.240 --> 22:44.400
I'm very happy

22:44.400 --> 22:45.660
says the leopard

22:46.440 --> 22:47.620
and I'm hungry

22:48.440 --> 22:49.460
let's go hunting

22:50.160 --> 22:51.960
yes good idea

22:51.960 --> 22:53.200
says the man

